### Run Python
POST http://127.0.0.1:8766/mcp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 1,
  "method": "run_python",
  "params": { "code": "print('hi from MCP')" }
}

### List Files
POST http://127.0.0.1:8766/mcp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 2,
  "method": "list_files",
  "params": { "path": "." }
}

### SQL Query
POST http://127.0.0.1:8766/mcp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 3,
  "method": "sql_query",
  "params": { "query": "select * from notes" }
}
